description:
Job Description
We are looking for a strong problem solvers with passion towards development and self learning.
As a part of the team, you will be responsible for designing and developing web applications. You will also handle delivery of end-to-end systems from analysis, design, implementation, quality assurance to delivery.
Develop and maintain server-side logic and APIs for seamless integration with front-end components;
Collaborate closely with UI/UX designers to translate design mock-ups and wireframes into responsive, interactive web applications;
Conduct code reviews, provide constructive feedback, and mentor junior team members to foster a culture of continuous improvement and knowledge sharing;
Troubleshoot and debug complex issues in production environments, providing timely resolution and ensuring minimal downtime;
Architect, design, and implement scalable and reliable full-stack solutions using Node.js & Next.js/React.js, ensuring high performance and responsiveness;
You would be a perfect fit if you are/have:
Avid problem-solver with strong analytical skills, loves tackling complex technical challenges;
Thorough knowledge of software development best practices and design patterns, ensuring high-quality code and maintainability;
Preferred Tech stack: Strong in Node with either React or Next experience.
Individual as well as team contributor
